column.name: TRANSACTION_TYPE
column.comment: The type of the transaction.

column.name: HEADER_IDENT_STRING
column.comment: N/A

column.name: CORRECTION_FLAG
column.comment: Correction flag. Will be set to the value how the record should be merged to the existing records. (-1 delete; +1 add)

column.name: EXTRACTION_START_DATE
column.comment: N/A

column.name: EXTRACTION_END_DATE
column.comment: N/A

column.name: RUN_DATE_TIME
column.comment: N/A

column.name: MARKET_ID
column.comment: ID for the market provided by Provis in the header. 'MMO' for the MMO and MMC markets, 'PUA' for the PUA and PUC markets.

column.name: NEW_LINE1
column.comment: N/A

column.name: TRAILER_IDENT_STRING
column.comment: N/A

column.name: NUMBER_OF_LINES_BODY
column.comment: Only Arcor.

column.name: CREATION_DATETIME
column.comment: Creation date of the transaction.

column.name: EFFECTIVE_DATE
column.comment: The effective Date of the Email Validation - The Access Information is effective dated.

column.name: BACK_DATE
column.comment: Back-dated TRANSACTION_EFFECTIVE_DATE. Failed transactions will be corrected and delivered late. The actual TRANSACTION_EFFECTIVE_DATE is written in the TRANSACTION_BACK_DATE. The TRANSACTION_EFFECTIVE_DATE is in this

column.name: MAN
column.comment: MAN number of Service Provider

column.name: BAN
column.comment: Indication of the customer's billing account number. The customer is the (natural or legal) person to whom services are provided on the basis of a contract concluded with D2-Vodafone. For himself or others to him

column.name: SUBSCRIBER_NO
column.comment: Participant number

column.name: NAME
column.comment: !!! PLEASE REPAIR !!! - Here: content of the action.

column.name: NETWORK_PROVIDER_INDICATOR
column.comment: Indicates whether the business entity is the network provider or just a service provider of the cellular company.

column.name: ACCOUNT_TYPE
column.comment: Account type

column.name: ACCOUNT_SUB_TYPE
column.comment: Subset of the account type

column.name: PRE_PAID_INDICATOR
column.comment: Indicates wether the subscriber's BAN has a prepaid (debit) account, credit account or callya roaming account. Valid values are:  Y - prepaid, R - prepaid roaming, N - credit.

column.name: REPLENISHED_INDICATOR
column.comment: Indicates if replenishment of a prepaid subscriber is allowed.

column.name: SIM_CARD_NUMBER
column.comment: Indication of the serial number of the D2 card. When a telephone with a card is sold, the number of the new D2 card is shown here, and when a subsidized telephone is sold to an existing customer, the number of the customer's existing D2 card is shown here

column.name: SIM_CARD_TYPE
column.comment: The code of the SIM type.

column.name: FIRST_ACTIVATION_DATE
column.comment: The date which is set when the CUSTOMER`s state becomes Active for the first time(even if the service has been terminated).

column.name: ORIGINAL_SALES_FORCE_ID
column.comment: ID of the activating sales force

column.name: SERVICING_SALES_FORCE_ID
column.comment: Sales-force-id which performed the current transaction.

column.name: TARIFF_OPTION
column.comment: TARIFF_OPTION from KIAS2000

column.name: TARIFF_CODE
column.comment: TARIFF Code

column.name: TARIFF_TAKTUNG
column.comment: TARIFF CLOCK

column.name: CONTRACT_TYPE
column.comment:
The contract type associated with the SOC, refers to CONTRACT_TYPE table. - I = insert SOC
U = replace SOC
D = Delete SOC

column.name: COMMITMENT_PERIOD
column.comment: Number of committed contract months.

column.name: PRICE_PLAN
column.comment: Clear key for the participant's price plan.

column.name: INITIAL_AMOUNT_EUR
column.comment: For CallYa packages and CallYa boxes contains the amount of the starting credit  in euros and cents).

column.name: PAYMENT_METHOD
column.comment: The payment method of the BAN. Valid values: "DD" - direct debit, "CA" - cash, "CC" - credit card, "MT" - money transfer.

column.name: ACTIVATION_ORIGIN
column.comment: F - Fax (not in use), B - On-Line (CSM)

column.name: MATCH_CODE
column.comment: Match code on itemised commission bill for further queries. The match code value of the ASPC interface will be populated in this field.

column.name: SOC
column.comment: Service Order Code, der zur Berechnung des zum Merkmal gehörenden Betrages verwendet wird.

column.name: SECONDARY_MSISDN
column.comment: The number assigned to the secondary service.

column.name: CARD_OWNED_BY_SUBSCRIBER_IND
column.comment: 'Y'-yes, 'N'-no

column.name: CANCELLATION_DATE
column.comment: Notice date. If SUBSCRIBER_ALL.SUBSCRIBER_STATUS_ACTIVITY = CAN, the SUBSCRIBER_STATUS_DATE from the table SUBSCRIBER_ALL is inserted, otherwise NULL

column.name: CANCELLATION_REASON
column.comment: The reason specified by the customer on the cancellation request. Refers to the reference table CANCELLATION_REASON. - Cancellation Reason Code

column.name: RESUME_REASON
column.comment: Reason for reactivation.

column.name: GROUP_ID
column.comment: Invoice item group ID

column.name: COMMITMENT_PERIOD_START_DATE
column.comment: Start Date of the commitment.

column.name: COMMITMENT_PERIOD_END_DATE
column.comment: End Date of the commitment.

column.name: LINE_TYPE
column.comment: Only Arcor. The values are derived from the product-type of the subscriber as follows: ISD <-> S0-M, ANL <-> A, PMX <-> S2M, BAA <-> S0-A

column.name: NUMBER_OF_LINES
column.comment: Only Arcor.

column.name: RESERVE_DATE
column.comment: Only Arcor.

column.name: OLD_VALUE
column.comment: Previous Value in case of subscriber changes.

column.name: PREL_FINAL_IND
column.comment: P -> preliminary record in Dwh, F -> final record in Dwh

column.name: DEACT_DELAY
column.comment: Number of months between activation and deactivation. The field is only filled for permanent deactivations.

column.name: SEGMENT_STATUS
column.comment: Status of a NL and/or segment change

column.name: PRECEDING_PROLONGATION_DATE
column.comment: The date of the preceding prolongation.

column.name: SPECIAL_PERMISSION_REASON
column.comment: The reason for the special permission (if given).

column.name: END_DAY_OF_GRACE_PERIOD
column.comment: The end date of the grace period. This field is relevant only if the PP is at the BAN level and includes minimum requirements.

column.name: SUBSIDY_TYPE
column.comment: Type of the subsidy

column.name: MARKET_CODE
column.comment: Market to which the customer is assigned. Examples are MMC (credit customers who have a contract with VfD2), PUC (credit customers who have a contract with a partner company), MMO (prepaid customers who are directly assigned to VfD2), PUA (prepdaid customers

column.name: PRODUCT_TYPE
column.comment: Identifies the participant's product type (e.g. GSM).

column.name: TRANSFER_DAY
column.comment: Arrival of the transaction booking (corresponds to the time dimension from VISS)

column.name: NBA_TIP_FLAG
column.comment: Indicator for matching NBA-Tip, valid values 0 and 1.

column.name: ZIP_CODE
column.comment: The area code.

column.name: PACKAGE_ITEM_ID
column.comment: If the serial number is part of a package, this is the package item_id.

column.name: REGISTRATION_SALES_FORCE_ID
column.comment: Sales Force ID that registered the Call Ya subscriber's postcard; only valid for Call Ya subscribers with unregistered postcards.

column.name: INITIAL_AMOUNT_INCL_TAX_IND
column.comment: Inidicates if the initial amounts includes tax. Valid values: Y - the initial amount includes Tax, N - the initial amount does not include Tax

column.name: CALL_YA_TYPE
column.comment: "B" -> CallYa-Box, "P" -> CallYa-Package.

column.name: SUBSIDISED_PHONE
column.comment: Indicates if the contract renewal included a subsidised phone. Valid values: J - The contract renewal included a subsidised phone, N - The contract renewal did not include a subsidised phone

column.name: OEM_SALES_FORCE_ID
column.comment: The ID of the OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) that sold the equipment to the subscriber.

column.name: NEW_LINE
column.comment: N/A
